eu.jgen.beegen.model.api

Class JGenModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.jgen.beegen.model.api.JGenModel

  • public class JGenModel
extends java.lang.Object
    This object represents a model stored in the container. A container connects to the SQLite database for accessing model data.

    1.0.0
    Author:
    Marek Stankiewicz

      • JGenModel

        public JGenModel(JGenContainer genContainer)
        The class contractor creates an instance of the model object and associates the model object with the container. Container knows how to access the SQLite database to retrieve information about objects and their associations and properties.
        Parameters:
        genContainer - reference to the container object
